<section xml:id="Grading">

  <title>Grading</title>
  
   <subsection>
      <title>Problem 1</title>

      <p>
        Convert the following quadratic function to vertex form (<m> f(x)=a(x-h)^2+k  </m>).  State the vertex.  Further, state the domain and range.  

        <me> f(x)=x^2+12x-15</me>
      </p>
    

    </subsection>

    <subsection>
    <title>Problem 2</title>

      <p>
        No makeup assignments here, but I will drop your lowest two quiz scores.  
      </p>
    </subsection>


